{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji21","name":"毛泽东全集第21卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji21.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给毛岸青的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给毛岸青的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年1月7日）岸青，我的亲爱的儿："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"岸英回国，收到你的信，知道你的情形，很是欢喜。看见你哥哥，好像看见你一样，希望你在那里继续学习，将来学成回国，好为人民服务。你妹妹（李讷²）问候你，她现已五岁半。她的剪纸，寄你两张。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝你进步，愉快，成长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九四六年一月七日[1]毛岸青，当时在苏联学习。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1946,"month":1,"day":7}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":133,"page_end":133},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}